{"type": "article", "id": 30352, "title": "火焰音响", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-31T22:57:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160731204447LexHj2zpYIyE13Uh.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>既然水柱能用来展现音乐的变化，火焰是不是也可以？美国俄勒冈州单人设计工作室 Grey Street Design 最近推出了一款火焰音响 <a href=\"http://firesideaudiobox.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fireside Audiobox</a>，铝制的圆柱形燃烧器会随着乐曲的声波和频率喷出对应的橙色火苗，带给人一种奇特的视听感受。燃烧器由一个钢化玻璃罩进行保护，下方则是竹子制成的音箱，整个设备由内置的锂电池进行供电。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/firesideaudiobox/fireside-audiobox-light-your-music-on-fire\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 349 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731204505otfqOEXn9HlsCmpV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731204504cT7wHCX5kbNrnlV2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.616176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731204505Uurx5pHgM9w07oQA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.546455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160731204507yrN2Is8Qf3Jxok0v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}